text: Najib Azmi Mikati (; born 24 November 1955) is a Lebanese politician. In 2021, he became the Prime Minister of Lebanon. He was the prime minister before twice, from April 2005 to July 2005 and again from 2011 to 2014. He was also the Acting President of Lebanon from 2022 to 2025. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Lebanon Category:Presidents of Lebanon
title: Najib Mikati
